    <entry>
      <title>小技巧</title>
      <link href="/2021/12/13/xiao-ji-qiao/"/>
      <url>/2021/12/13/xiao-ji-qiao/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol><li><p>```html<br>h$*6&gt;{$级标题} </p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   用来快速打出多个标题；</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">2. lorem,乱数假文，没有任何实际含义的文字，通常用这个来测试排版；</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">3.速写父子兄弟元素</span><br><span class="line">```html</span><br><span class="line">(h2&gt;a+div)*2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>锚链接</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a[href=&quot;#chapter$&quot;]*6&gt;&#123;章节$&#125;</span><br><span class="line">((h2[id=&quot;chapter$&quot;]&gt;&#123;章节$&#125;)+p&gt;lorem1000)*6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;#&quot;</span>&gt;</span>回到顶部<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
